<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink319">
<l>kaṇpora viḷaṅkiya katirteṟu vaippiṉ</l>
<l>maṇpurai perukiya maramuḷi kāṉa</l>
<l>miṟantaṉa rōnaṅ kātalar</l>
<l>maṟantaṉa rōti maṟavā nammē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Our lover has traversed the forest where parched trees </l>
<l>grow from the sand mounds in the region  </l>
<l>scorched by sunrays that shine to blind eyes. </l>
<l>Alas! Has he forgotten us, who are not forgetting him? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
